ng was fixed.3. I love the fact that I get to be the antichrist and murder people. (Basically, I love the Omen and the concept of the two Lucius games) I know the first game was definitely parallel to the Omen in story but Lucius II had an original storyline in continuation of the first game.And regardless of the flaws of this game, I'm looking forward to a Lucius III."
